  "title": "LICENSED PLUMBER",
  "description": "<p>- Obtained a valid Plumber License with PUB in Singapore.</p><p>- Installation, repair and servicing of water pipes,\nplumbing fixtures and sanitary works.</p><p>- Ensure work performed on site comply with the local\nauthority (PUB) requirements for site works and submissions.</p><p>- Liaising with authorities</p><p>- attend meetings with supplier, sub-contractor, main\ncontractor, consultant, and authority</p><p>- submit reports</p><p>- To attend\ncustomer place site survey and notification to PUB portal for water tank\nwashing, repair work and installation.</p><p>- During tank washing time, spot check and after sampling result need to submit PUB\nportal.</p><p>- If sanitation system installation, then PUB portable notification and after job\ncompletion PUB submission </p><p>- Ensuring all plumbing work complies with safety standards\nand building codes.<br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Certification:     Must possess a valid PUB Plumber License.</li><li>Experience:  2 – 5 years of relevant experience in plumbing installation, maintenance, and repairs.</li><li>Proven knowledge of Singapore's plumbing standards, codes, and regulations.</li><li>Strong  attention to detail and excellent problem-solving skills.</li><li>Ability to work independently as well as part of a team.</li><li>Good communication skills and ability to collaborate effectively with contractors and other professionals.</li><li>Physically fit and able to handle the demands of the job.</li><li>A proactive and responsible work ethic with a strong commitment to safety.</li></ul>",
